description: The QVine app allows you to ask about upcoming events on the QVine calendar.  You can ask about the quarterly meetings, picnic, holiday party, other corporate activities and holidays.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask QVine, when is the next quarterly meeting?
Alexa, ask QVine, when is the next holiday?
Alexa, ask QVine, when is the next corporate activity?
name: QVine
shortDescription: This app allows QVine employees to ask about upcoming events on the QVine calendar.
